  discard plugin  This plugin will discard a message by pretending that the message was queued.  It is designed to be used by other plugins which request the message be
discard by setting a connection or transaction note that this plugin
checks.  It uses the 'queue' hook, so it runs after all the plugins that hook on   data_post .  If you use the 'quarantine' plug-in then this plugin should run   after  it.  USE THIS PLUGIN WITH CARE!  Enable  Enable by adding a   queue/discard  entry in   config/plugins    before  your
other queue plugins that perform actual deliveries.  Usage  Set     connection.notes.discard   =   [   1   |   true   ];
  or     connection.transaction.notes.discard   =   [   1   |   true   ];
